    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and no imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, with leather that is supple and free of any wear, and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no pending maintenance needs. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and treated with the utmost care.",
