    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dents, and the paint is starting to fade in some areas. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear, including some minor staining and a small tear in the driver's seat. While the car runs and drives well, it does have a few minor mechanical quirks that will eventually need attention, and the tires will likely need replacing within the next year. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that is priced to reflect its current state and the work a new owner might want to put into it.",
      "price": 20000.0,
