      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs great and is ready for its next adventure with you! I\u2019m super easy to work with, so feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take a look. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 29500.0,
