      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, featuring the M96.03 3.6L flat-six engine and the sought-after 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. This wide-body C4S utilizes the Turbo-spec chassis and 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc fixed calipers for superior deceleration and thermal capacity. To ensure long-term reliability, the IMS bearing has been retrofitted with an LN Engineering dual-row solution, and the Rear Main Seal (RMS) was replaced during the last clutch service. The viscous-coupling AWD system provides exceptional lateral grip, and the suspension maintains factory-spec damping characteristics. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is dialed-in for immediate high-performance use. A true driver\u2019s car with all critical preventative maintenance documented.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
