    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and pride of ownership. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, showing only the lightest signs of road use, with no major dents or scratches to detract from its silhouette. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the premium upholstery is clean and firm, the dashboard is free of sun damage, and every button and switch operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced religiously at scheduled intervals, with a comprehensive log of recent work including a cooling system refresh and a new set of all-season tires. On the road, it handles with confidence\u2014no rattles, no leaks, and a smooth, powerful acceleration that confirms its mechanical integrity. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has clearly been loved.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
